libpisp-rpi (1.5.0-1~noble1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Initial release under the cleaner name `libpisp-rpi`. The earlier
    `libpisp-rpi-local` source package is superseded — "-local" was a
    leftover from the GitHub Releases-only phase and no longer reflects
    the package shipping via the Launchpad PPA.
  * Unofficial Ubuntu build of upstream libpisp at
    raspberrypi/libpisp@07e61ad07596b4c5729289e9016ec19fea7f0d19,
    for Raspberry Pi 5 PiSP support on Ubuntu 24.04 (Noble).

 -- Dmitri Manajev <dmitri@manajev.com>  Sun, 24 May 2026 12:00:00 +0000
